[This event of atypical BSE in Brazil was already covered in ProMED-mail posting 20190602.6499721.

The OIE recognizes Brazil as a country having negligible risk status for BSE. Cases of atypical BSE do not impact the official BSE risk status of a country, and therefore, this latest detection will not change the negligible risk status of Brazil. - Mod.CRD

